: center;"><span class="C9DxTc " style="font-size: 15.0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">Fun, Entertaining, and Usable by all ages. Even infants love this product!</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-c5RTEf Ft7HRd-AhqUyc-c5RTEf purZT-AhqUyc-c5RTEf ZcASvf-AhqUyc-c5RTEf pSzOP-AhqUyc-c5RTEf Ktthjf-AhqUyc-c5RTEf JNdkSc SQVYQc yYI8W HQwdzb"><div class="JNdkSc-SmKAyb LkDMRd"><div class="" jscontroller="sGwD4d" jsaction="zXBUYb:zTPCnb;zQF9Uc:Qxe3nd;" jsname="F57UId"><div class="oKdM2c ZZyype Kzv0Me"><div id="h.6efad567a946b419_54" class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-c5RTEf Ft7HRd-AhqUyc-c5RTEf purZT-AhqUyc-c5RTEf ZcASvf-AhqUyc-c5RTEf pSzOP-AhqUyc-c5RTEf Ktthjf-AhqUyc-c5RTEf jXK9ad D2fZ2 zu5uec OjCsFc dmUFtb"><div class="jXK9ad-SmKAyb"><div class="tyJCtd baZpAe"><div class="t3iYD"><img src="./Cat_files/unnamed(3).jpg" class="CENy8b" role="img" style="width: 100%; margin: 0% 0 0% 0%"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="oKdM2c ZZyype"><div id="h.6efad567a946b419_39" class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-c5RTEf Ft7HRd-AhqUyc-c5RTEf purZT-AhqUyc-c5RTEf ZcASvf-AhqUyc-c5RTEf pSzOP-AhqUyc-c5RTEf Ktthjf-AhqUyc-c5RTEf jXK9ad D2fZ2 zu5uec wHaque g5GTcb"><div class="jXK9ad-SmKAyb"><div class="tyJCtd mGzaTb Depvyb baZpAe"><p dir="ltr" class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke " style="text-align: center;"><span class="C9DxTc " style="font-size: 15.0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">The product has been tested and made to make your home secure both physically and digitally!</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-c5RTEf Ft7HRd-AhqUyc-c5RTEf purZT-AhqUyc-c5RTEf ZcASvf-AhqUyc-c5RTEf pSzOP-AhqUyc-c5RTEf Ktthjf-AhqUyc-c5RTEf JNdkSc SQVYQc yYI8W HQwdzb"><div class="JNdkSc-SmKAyb LkDMRd"><div class="" jscontroller="sGwD4d" jsaction="zXBUYb:zTPCnb;zQF9Uc:Qxe3nd;" jsname="F57UId"><div class="oKdM2c ZZyype Kzv0Me"><div id="h.6efad567a946b419_68" class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-c5RTEf Ft7HRd-AhqUyc-c5RTEf purZT-AhqUyc-c5RTEf ZcASvf-AhqUyc-c5RTEf pSzOP-AhqUyc-c5RTEf Ktthjf-AhqUyc-c5RTEf jXK9ad D2fZ2 zu5uec OjCsFc dmUFtb"><div class="jXK9ad-SmKAyb"><div class="tyJCtd baZpAe"><div class="t3iYD"><img src="./Cat_files/unnamed(4).jpg" class="CENy8b" role="img"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="oKdM2c ZZyype"><div id="h.6efad567a946b419_44" class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-c5RTEf Ft7HRd-AhqUyc-c5RTEf purZT-AhqUyc-c5RTEf ZcASvf-AhqUyc-c5RTEf pSzOP-AhqUyc-c5RTEf Ktthjf-AhqUyc-c5RTEf jXK9ad D2fZ2 zu5uec wHaque g5GTcb"><div class="jXK9ad-SmKAyb"><div class="tyJCtd mGzaTb Depvyb baZpAe"><p dir="ltr" class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke " style="text-align: center;"><span class="C9DxTc " style="font-size: 15.0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">Each product is made with a unique battery type that allows the bot to function to the fullest of its ability</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="h.6efad567a946b419_84" class="yaqOZd"><div class="IFuOkc"></div><div class="mYVXT"><div class="LS81yb VICjCf j5pSsc db35Fc" tabindex="-1"><div class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd Ft7HRd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd purZT-AhqUyc-II5mzb ZcASvf-AhqUyc-II5mzb pSzOP-AhqUyc-qWD73c Ktthjf-AhqUyc-qWD73c JNdkSc SQVYQc"><div class="JNdkSc-SmKAyb LkDMRd"><div class="" jscontroller="sGwD4d" jsaction="zXBUYb:zTPCnb;zQF9Uc:Qxe3nd;" jsname="F57UId"><div class="oKdM2c ZZyype Kzv0Me"><div id="h.6efad567a946b419_81" class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd Ft7HRd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd jXK9ad D2fZ2 zu5uec OjCsFc dmUFtb wHaque g5GTcb"><div class="jXK9ad-SmKAyb"><div class="tyJCtd mGzaTb Depvyb baZpAe"><div id="h.amh36r6uprkq" class="Ap4VC yMxPgf  aP9Z7e"></div><h1 id="h.amh36r6uprkq_l" dir="ltr" class="zfr3Q duRjpb CDt4Ke " style="text-align: center;"><div jscontroller="Ae65rd" jsaction="touchstart:UrsOsc; click:KjsqPd; focusout:QZoaZ; mouseover:y0pDld; mouseout:dq0hvd;fv1Rjc:jbFSOd;CrfLRd:SzACGe;" class="CjVfdc"><div class="PPhIP rviiZ" jsname="haAclf"><div role="presentation" class="U26fgb mUbCce fKz7Od LRAOtb Znu9nd M9Bg4d" jscontroller="mxS5xe" jsaction="click:cOuCgd; mousedown:UX7yZ; mouseup:lbsD7e; mouseenter:tfO1Yc; mouseleave:JywGue; focus:AHmuwe; blur:O22p3e; contextmenu:mg9Pef;" jsshadow="" aria-describedby="h.amh36r6uprkq_l" aria-label="Copy heading link" aria-disabled="false" data-tooltip="Copy heading link" aria-hidden="true" data-tooltip-position="top" data-tooltip-vertical-offset="12" data-tooltip-horizontal-offset="0"><a class="FKF6mc TpQm9d" href="https://sites.google.com/mcvts.org/parvumprotectors/home#h.amh36r6uprkq" aria-label="Copy heading link" jsname="hiK3ld" role="button" aria-describedby="h.amh36r6uprkq_l"><div class="VTBa7b MbhUzd" jsname="ksKsZd"></div><span jsslot="" class="xjKiLb"><span class="Ce1Y1c" style="top: -11px"><svg class="OUGEr QdAdhf" width="22px" height="22px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" focusable="false"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"></path></svg></span></span></a></div></div><span class="C9DxTc " style="color: #000000;">Sharing Experiences</span></div></h1><p dir="ltr" class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke " style="text-align: center;"><span class="C9DxTc " style="font-size: 15.0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">Here at Solveance, we don't just want to share our products, we want to share experiences.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke " style="text-align: center;"><span class="C9DxTc " style="font-size: 15.0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">The Parvum Protectors were created to prevent deaths in home robberies, especially in homes with children.</span></p><p dir="ltr" class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke " style="text-align: center;"><span class="C9DxTc " style="font-size: 15.0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">The story that helped inspire us to create this product comes from the CEO themselves who lost their kids during a home robbery and now has devoted themselves to make the world a better and safer place.</span></p><p dir="ltr" class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke " style="text-align: center;"><span class="C9DxTc " style="font-size: 8.0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">This is a fictional story. Please do not take this seriously!!</span><span class="C9DxTc " style="font-size: 15.0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="h.6efad567a946b419_94" class="yaqOZd"><div class="IFuOkc"></div><div class="mYVXT"><div class="LS81yb VICjCf j5pSsc db35Fc" tabindex="-1"><div class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd Ft7HRd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd purZT-AhqUyc-II5mzb ZcASvf-AhqUyc-II5mzb pSzOP-AhqUyc-qWD73c Ktthjf-AhqUyc-qWD73c JNdkSc SQVYQc yYI8W HQwdzb"><div class="JNdkSc-SmKAyb LkDMRd"><div class="" jscontroller="sGwD4d" jsaction="zXBUYb:zTPCnb;zQF9Uc:Qxe3nd;" jsname="F57UId"><div class="oKdM2c ZZyype Kzv0Me"><div id="h.6efad567a946b419_91" class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd Ft7HRd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd jXK9ad D2fZ2 zu5uec OjCsFc dmUFtb"><div class="jXK9ad-SmKAyb"><div class="tyJCtd mGzaTb Depvyb baZpAe"><div id="h.q1g3ggx7864m" class="Ap4VC yMxPgf  aP9Z7e"></div><h1 id="h.q1g3ggx7864m_l" dir="ltr" class="zfr3Q duRjpb CDt4Ke " style="text-align: center;"><div jscontroller="Ae65rd" jsaction="touchstart:UrsOsc; click:KjsqPd; focusout:QZoaZ; mouseover:y0pDld; mouseout:dq0hvd;fv1Rjc:jbFSOd;CrfLRd:SzACGe;" class="CjVfdc"><div class="PPhIP rviiZ" jsname="haAclf"><div role="presentation" class="U26fgb mUbCce fKz7Od LRAOtb Znu9nd M9Bg4d" jscontroller="mxS5xe" jsaction="click:cOuCgd; mousedown:UX7yZ; mouseup:lbsD7e; mouseenter:tfO1Yc; mouseleave:JywGue; focus:AHmuwe; blur:O22p3e; contextmenu:mg9Pef;" jsshadow="" aria-describedby="h.q1g3ggx7864m_l" aria-label="Copy heading link" aria-disabled="false" data-tooltip="Copy heading link" aria-hidden="true" data-tooltip-position="top" data-tooltip-vertical-offset="12" data-tooltip-horizontal-offset="0"><a class="FKF6mc TpQm9d" href="https://sites.google.com/mcvts.org/parvumprotectors/home#h.q1g3ggx7864m" aria-label="Copy heading link" jsname="hiK3ld" role="button" aria-describedby="h.q1g3ggx7864m_l"><div class="VTBa7b MbhUzd" jsname="ksKsZd"></div><span jsslot="" class="xjKiLb"><span class="Ce1Y1c" style="top: -11px"><svg class="OUGEr QdAdhf" width="22px" height="22px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" focusable="false"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"></path></svg></span></span></a></div></div><span class="C9DxTc " style="color: #000000;">Basic Model Options</span></div></h1><p dir="ltr" class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke " style="text-align: center;"><span class="C9DxTc " style="font-size: 15.0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">These options include; Cat, Bunny, and Dog</span></p><p dir="ltr" class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke " style="text-align: center;"><span class="C9DxTc " style="font-size: 15.0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">Other options are available but prices vary depending on the model. The basic models all go for $99.99 while other options range from $100 - $300 dollars.</span></p><p dir="ltr" class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke " style="text-align: center;"><span class="C9DxTc " style="font-size: 15.0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">If you need inspiration or want to see available options for a Parvum Protector, see the Concept Carousel Below.</span></p><br></div></div></div></div><div class="oKdM2c ZZyype"><div id="h.6efad567a946b419_99" class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd Ft7HRd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd jXK9ad D2fZ2 zu5uec wHaque g5GTcb"><div class="jXK9ad-SmKAyb"><div class="tyJCtd mGzaTb Depvyb baZpAe"><div id="h.91f799y6ubx7" class="Ap4VC yMxPgf  aP9Z7e"></div><h1 id="h.91f799y6ubx7_l" dir="ltr" class="zfr3Q duRjpb CDt4Ke " style="text-align: center;"><div jscontroller="Ae65rd" jsaction="touchstart:UrsOsc; click:KjsqPd; focusout:QZoaZ; mouseover:y0pDld; mouseout:dq0hvd;fv1Rjc:jbFS